structure.unit: FEES AND COMPENSATION OF PUBLIC OFFICERS AND EMPLOYEES

law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) ch. 14, sec. 491, effective January 2, 1978. -- Amended 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 311, sec. 1. -- Amended 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 152, sec. 29. -- Created 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 81, secs. 1 and 2.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Justices of the peace in counties of less than 250,000 population -- Compensation -- Return of fees.
